/**
 * Quick Actions Floating Action Button (Task 8-b: Feature 2)
 * ------------------------------------------------------------------
 * A fixed-position FAB in the bottom-right corner of the viewport that
 * expands into a vertical stack of 5-6 quick action buttons with
 * staggered slide-up animation. The FAB:
 *   - Uses an amber Sparkles icon as the main button
 *   - Pulses softly while idle (custom `fab-pulse-amber` keyframes)
